  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es erst einmal wunderbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.120", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es zu einer fr\u00fchen Stunde an prominenter Stelle eine solche Debatte gibt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.760", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Religionsfreiheit weltweit ist bedroht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
