   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.120", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und darauf m\u00fcssen wir hinweisen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.840", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben dieser Tage erlebt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auch die Religionsfreiheit in unserem Land bedroht ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.360", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Volker Kauder und andere Kollegen haben bei \u201eBerlin tr\u00e4gt Kippa\u201c demonstriert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.480", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist f\u00fcr uns ein Akt der Solidarit\u00e4t\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.120", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr uns leider nur ein Akt der Solidarit\u00e4t;\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist f\u00fcr uns ungef\u00e4hrlich\u00a0\u2013; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.280", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.440", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.240", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie durch die Stra\u00dfen laufen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.040", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem allt\u00e4glichen Antisemitismus konfrontiert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
