   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.040", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es kann nicht sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.560", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auch in unserem Land die Religionsfreiheit nicht gelebt werden kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.600", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen uns f\u00fcr diese Menschen einsetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.200", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.400", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass mein eigener Glaube nicht nur Privatsache ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.320", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das h\u00f6rt man dieser Tage h\u00e4ufig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.960", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will meinen Glauben durchaus auch im \u00f6ffentlichen Raum ausleben k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Symbol daf\u00fcr ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.680", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man im \u00f6ffentlichen Raum Kippa tragen kann und sich damit nicht sozusagen in das Hinterzimmer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.640", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
